\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (...What is this? There's a small
hemispherical metal pole with bumps and
indentations scattered on it.)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (It's a camera for shooting... Could it
be that we're using this to film that video?)
\n<Udo Takeru>Nfufufu, hey, over here, everything is ready~♪

......I'm not convinced. The doubts haven't
cleared either.

For the sake of work... for the sake of playing a
role, and to not disappoint everyone's
expectations. Convenient reasons to affirm oneself
\r[ intertwine in my mind.

\#......I knelt down like last night. \# And then,
provocatively, I reached out towards the throbbing
manhood----....
\n<Udo Takeru>Nfufufu, look, everything is ready over here~♪

......I'm not convinced. The doubts haven't

For the sake of work... for the sake of playing a

then, as if teasing, I reached out towards the
throbbing manhood----....
